Responsibilities:
Process Interco back charge billing and Interco Payable invoices.
Prepare monthly journals, bank reconciliation and balance sheet schedules.
Prepare tax schedules and statutory reports.
Assist in yearly internal and external audits.
Able to handle GST returns.
Requirements:
Diploma in Accountancy.
Preferably with 2 to 3 years working experience with corporate reporting responsibilities.
Good interpersonal skills, meticulous and able to handle tight deadlines.
Preferably with experience in Oracle, JDE Accounting and Hyperion.